title: Resin “Experts” Test Viral Resin Hacks
author: Evan and Katelyn
description:
Y’all have been sending us viral resin hacks for years and it’s finally time to test them! Go to https://buyraycon.com/evanandkatelyn and use code HOLIDAY to get 15% off your Raycon order! Brought to you by Raycon. Check out the tools we used below! 👇

🙏 Other sponsors:
TotalBoat: check out the 2-part resin we use: http://totalboat.refr.cc/evankatelyn (search for high performance) (affiliate link)
Sophie & Toffee: check out the UVdiamond resin we use: https://sophieandtoffee.com/EvanandKatelyn 

Check out the Patreon Aftershow for:
- How many days it actually took to film
- Brainstorming a cursed egg project
- How we learned that sunlight can really warp thin resin
- What we really think about life hacks in general
- Our expectations vs how they turned out
- Looking back, would we do any life hacks differently?
- Why Katelyn chose the life hacks that she did
If you're a Patron already, watch it here: https://www.patreon.com/posts/resin-hacks-59757146
Not a Patron yet? Join here: https://www.patreon.com/evanandkatelyn
